	   <tr><td colspan=2> Ok Nits reporting in... heh<br>I have xplored every place any guide has reccomened for level 30. I trid hunting there at least for 2 hours and compared exp and loot of each. Following is a list of the places visited and comments about them:<br><br>Outside Paw: Loot was ok, exp wasnt all that great<br><br>Inside Paw: Better exp, a lil better loot, but it can get crowded with just 2 groups of 6.<br><br>Dwarves in OoT: This was one of the best exp's but it gets really boring. And loot was terrible.<br><br>Frontier Mountains: Not good exp for me at all, but the loot is hard to beat. The items you get can sell to a merchant for up to 65pp! <br><br>Rathe Mountains: Whether you are hunting Giant Skeletons or Hill Giants the exp wont be all that great.. but the money is hard to beat. Hill Giants CAN drop up to 60pp (thats the highest ive seen at one time) I didnt like RM personally though because of all the really high level NPC's wandering around. AT one point i got lost and got slughtered by a named Shpinx. She was a chanter and feared me and then killed me. Died 3 times getting my corpse back, if this happens to you, remember Wood Elfs arent KOS (dont know what other races arent)<br><br>Cazic Thule: This place is hard to beat.... great exp and great loot. I average about 150-250pp an hour here, and about 3 blue bubs of exp and hour. I originally left here, then came back and found out this WAS the best one. <br><br>Eastern Wastes: Great loot, but i died here more often then anywhere else. I wouldnt go here till level 40.<br><br>Iceclad Ocean: This is my 2nd choice. Great exp, a little bit of loot, and he chance of a cougar claw earring is great! If you prefer open areas over dungeons then go here.<br><br>I also travelled around other places, but these were the ones worth mentioning. Some of these places will keep you satisfied from level 24-35 (Cazic) and other will go from 30-45 (Eastern Wastes) but any one of these places will get you to level 34. Its really up to you....<br><br>Nitsujlak Barshemguud Ogre Shaman Of war!!<br>Prexus server<br>Please feel free to rate my posts, i love input =)<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
