	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you are a barbarian, kill the gnolls at the entrance to Black Burrows (and the ones inside the tunnel on the EF side of the zone).&nbsp;&nbsp;Save any gnoll fangs you loot.  You turn them in later to Captain Tillen at the arena in S Qeynos for xp and moonstones.  The moonstones you turn in at the bar where Trumpy Irontoe hangs out (can never remember the name of the bar or the guy you turn them into).  You'll get more xp and some blackburrow stout (get to work on the old alcohol tolerance! :)<br><br>When you don't get xp for the gnolls outside of BB, then it is time to step inside the nightmare for your xp (I never did like Black Burrows, but your only other option really is to pass on thru bb to Qeynos Hills and do the giant bats, etc, but then you'd miss all the trains!!).<br><br>You can hunt in BB until lvl 14 or 15, then it will be time to move on to new grounds.<br><br>Good luck!<br>&nbsp;<br>Badjur<br>54 Barbarian Shaman (Druzzil Ro)<br><br>Aepox Weeblatter<br>35 Dwarf Warrior</td></tr>
