	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Group with a necro, once you have cannibalize.&nbsp;&nbsp;Cast regen on the necro, and have them cast shadow compact on you constantly and drain the difference from your victims.  You can cast cannibalize almost constantly, and take continuous pulls without ever sitting down to med.  A shaman, a warrior, and my necro cleared the giant fort in warsliks that way, when all the giants there were still blue or higher.<br><br>After 30 or so, it's not worth it because you med so much faster than you used to, and the necro's 80 hp transfer doesn't seem like so much any more.  It will probably work again with 39+ shaman and 44+ necro using pact of shadow and cannibalize 2.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
